BEGIN NOW If truth be tried by these tongues, then whence should a Translation be made, but out of them? END
BEGIN NOW These tongues therefore, the Scriptures we say in those tongues, we set before us to translate, being the tongues wherein God was pleased to speak to his Church by the Prophets and Apostles. END
